title: ►Remodeled, flat, in a three-unit building
posting_body: ['TO VIEW THIS HOME:', 'Please reply by email to this posting.', 'Remodeled, flat, in a three-unit, private building.', 'Meticulously renovated flat, in the heart of Glen Park.', 'The unit boasts all hardwood (pergo) floors throughout the home.', 'One bedroom with generous closet space, a remodeled kitchen with stainless appliances, a beautifully finished bathroom, and rarely found in-unit washer and dryer.', 'Church Street Gourmet Ghetto, or Glen Park Village, resides just a few blocks away, with supermarkets, shops, popular cafes, and restaurants, convenient public transportation, and BART.', 'This home is a commuter dream with easy access to 101/280 freeways.', 'There is ample street parking.', 'There is a short commute to the financial district and many private and tech bus routes nearby.', 'Walk Score: 91', 'About you:', '1.', 'Clean credit.', '2.', 'First-month rent and a security deposit of ONE month rent.', '3.', 'The lease is for one year.', '4.', 'The move-in date is anytime in August or September 1st.', 'Thank you for reading this posting.', 'The lease agreement is at $2,999.', "Your average monthly rent is reduced to $2,799, with the first month's RENT FREE.", 'To schedule a private viewing, please reply by email to this posting.']
